CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12, reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh ...bottom, left to right; ...Robinson; Joyce...; Marion Harris; and Ethel...,... - Harris Photos"
